@anchor{Macro nth-value-or}
@deffn {Macro} {nth-value-or} nth-value @&body forms
@findex nth-value-or
Evaluates @code{form} arguments one at a time, until the @code{nth-value} returned by one
of the forms is true. It then returns all the values returned by evaluating
that form. If none of the forms return a true nth value, this form returns
@code{nil}.
@end deffn
